field_sponsoring_entity_kind%3A169">International Organization</a></div><div class="field-item odd"><a href="/en/browse/cases?f%5B0%5D=field_sponsoring_entity_kind%3A163">Non-Governmental Organization (Non-profit)</a></div></div></div><div class="field field-name-field-support-entity-kind-other field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above"><div class="field-label">Other: Supporting Entities:&nbsp;</div><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">See https://citizenspact.eu/about-project/partners/</div></div></div></div></div><div class="collapsible group-resources field-group-div speed-fast effect-none">
